<item><title>加拿大尼古丁袋无市场授权召回</title><link>https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/jia-na-da-ni-gu-ding-dai-wu-shi-chang-shou-quan-zhao-hui.html</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/jia-na-da-ni-gu-ding-dai-wu-shi-chang-shou-quan-zhao-hui.html</guid><description>加拿大卫生部发布尼古丁袋产品召回公告，该产品未获得加拿大药品识别号（DIN）市场授权，属于非法销售。卖家需立即停止销售并召回相关产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 03:43:59 +0000</pubDate><category>ban</category></item>
<item><title>加拿大卫生部警告：COHEALI木质奶嘴夹存在窒息风险</title><link>https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/jia-na-da-wei-sheng-bu-jing-gao-cohealimu-zhi-nai-zui-jia-cun-zai-zhi-xi-feng-xi.html</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/jia-na-da-wei-sheng-bu-jing-gao-cohealimu-zhi-nai-zui-jia-cun-zai-zhi-xi-feng-xi.html</guid><description>Health Canada发布召回警告，COHEALI木质奶嘴夹产品曾在Amazon.ca销售，针对3岁以下幼儿。产品螺钉松动可能导致儿童窒息风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 03:43:59 +0000</pubDate><category>recall</category></item>
<item><title>加拿大召回Wild West 96+ Strawberry Stampede液态钻石510雾化器因标签错误</title><link>https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/jia-na-da-zhao-hui-wild-west-96-strawberry-stampedeye-tai-zuan-shi-510wu-hua-qi.html</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/jia-na-da-zhao-hui-wild-west-96-strawberry-stampedeye-tai-zuan-shi-510wu-hua-qi.html</guid><description>CannaPiece Corp.召回Wild West 96+ Strawberry Stampede Liquid Diamonds 510 Vape产品。标签上的THC含量低于实际值，消费者可能因不了解准确THC水平而过量使用，导致过度醉酒和健康风险，包括混淆、思维紊乱、身心受损、焦虑、恐惧、血压下降、心率升高，严重情况可能导致精神病发作或住院。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 03:43:59 +0000</pubDate><category>labeling</category></item>
<item><title>Urban Shades 卷式窗帘因绞伤风险被召回</title><link>https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/urban-shades-juan-shi-chuang-lian-yin-jiao-shang-feng-xian-bei-zhao-hui.html</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/urban-shades-juan-shi-chuang-lian-yin-jiao-shang-feng-xian-bei-zhao-hui.html</guid><description>加拿大卫生部确定Urban Shades卷式窗帘不符合《有绳窗帘法规》，存在绞伤风险。幼儿可能拉动绳圈环绕颈部或被绳索缠绕，造成绞伤隐患。卫生部推荐使用无绳窗帘。截至2026年6月5日，加拿大未接到相关伤害报告。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 03:43:59 +0000</pubDate><category>recall</category></item>
<item><title>CPSC启动打击假冒安全标签专项执法，重点针对境外危险产品</title><link>https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/cpscqi-dong-da-ji-jia-mou-an-quan-biao-qian-zhuan-xiang-zhi-fa-zhong-dian-zhen-d.html</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://liyuyangli485-commits.github.io/global-compliance/2026-06-11/cpscqi-dong-da-ji-jia-mou-an-quan-biao-qian-zhuan-xiang-zhi-fa-zhong-dian-zhen-d.html</guid><description>2026年5月6日美国消费品安全委员会(CPSC)宣布启动打击假冒安全标签的专项执法行动，重点查处使用伪造UL、ETL等认证标识将危险境外产品推入美国家庭的行为。CPSC同步公开征求意见，以强化执法工具、堵塞被不法分子利用的监管漏洞，跨境电商卖家与进口商将面临更严的标签真伪及认证授权审查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 03:43:59 +0000</pubDate><category>labeling</category></item>
